subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Notre Dame will carry the sting of defeat from last year’s N.C.A.A. championship into their regional final against Maryland, who beat the 2011 winner Texas A&M on Sunday.
